    <title type="text">British Museum Collection Database Online</title>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="postMeta fix"> <span class="date"></span><a
      href="http://blog.britishmuseum.org/2012/12/07/introducing-our-new-fully-operational-beta-collection-search/">Introducing
      our new, fully-operational, beta collection&nbsp;search<strong><span
      class="contributor">&nbsp;</span></strong></a><br /><span
      style="font-size: x-small;"><span class="contributor">Matthew Cock, Head of web,
      British Museum</span></span><br /><span style="font-size:
      x-small;"><span class="contributor"><span class="date">December 7, 2012 • 4:24
      pm</span></span></span><br /><blockquote class="tr_bq"><span
      style="font-size: x-small;">In a recent post, I wrote about the launch of our <a
      href="http://britishmuseum.org/betacollectionsearch">new collection search beta</a>.
      Well, we’ve now gone a bit further, and released an overhaul of the ‘advanced search’
      functionality<a
      href="http://blog.britishmuseum.org/2012/12/07/introducing-our-new-fully-operational-beta-collection-search/">...</a></span></blockquote></div><br
      /><a href="http://www.britishmuseum.org/betacollectionsearch">Collection search
      (beta)</a><br /><br /><blockquote class="tr_bq"> <span
      style="font-size: x-small;">2,042,506 objects are available <br /> 711,896 of these
      have one or more images</span><br /><span style="font-size: x-small;">
      </span><div class="lightGrey"> <span style="font-size:
      x-small;"><em>Last updated: 2 December 2012</em></span>
      </div><span style="font-size: x-small;"> </span><div
      class="pullOut"><span style="font-size: x-small;">We are updating the design and
      functionality of the British Museum collection search.</span></div><span
      style="font-size: x-small;"></span><span style="font-size: x-small;">This Beta
      release includes a new-style search facility, with advanced functionality, and new layouts for
      search results, object pages and image galleries.</span><br /><span
      style="font-size: x-small;"></span><span style="font-size:
      x-small;"><span>Please note that there is a small chance&nbsp;the record for an
      object on the beta is out-of-date. To be sure that you are getting the latest version of the
      data, please use the</span><a class="darkGrey"
      href="http://www.britishmuseum.org/research/search_the_collection_database.aspx">full
      version of the collection search</a></span><br /><span style="font-size:
      x-small;"> </span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a class="darkGrey"
      href="http://blog.britishmuseum.org/2012/08/31/searching-the-british-museum-collection/">Read
      more about this on our blog</a> and if you have any&nbsp;feedback or questions about
      the new design and functionality please&nbsp;either comment on the post or email <a
      class="darkGrey"
      href="mailto:web@britishmuseum.org">web@britishmuseum.org</a>&nbsp;with COL BETA
      in your subject line.</span></blockquote>]]></content>
